OL,3,CMotorbike overtook vehicle before head-
OL,4,Con crash that killed six, inquest told
OL,6,FAn inquest has heard how six people
OL,7,Fdied after a motorcycle overtook
OL,8,Fanother vehicle before colliding head-
OL,9,Fon with a car carrying a family of
OL,10,Ffour.
OL,12,FShane Roller and Shannen Morgan, along
OL,13,Fwith their daughters Rubie and Lillie,
OL,14,Fdied when the Ford Focus they were in
OL,15,Fwas involved in a collision on the A61
OL,16,Fbetween Wakefield and Barnsley.
OL,18,FTwo people on a BMW motorbike, lorry
OL,19,Fdriver Christopher Barton and his wife
OL,20,FJanine, also died.
