OL,3,CMotorbike overtook vehicle before head-
OL,4,Con crash that killed six, inquest told
OL,6,FAn inquest opened in Wakefield on
OL,7,FWednesday, 7 August, heard the
OL,8,Fincident happened on a 50mph stretch
OL,9,Fof the road at around 3.50pm on 21
OL,10,FJuly.
OL,12,FCoroner's support officer Phil Marr
OL,13,Ftold the court: "The collision
OL,14,Foccurred as the motorcycle was
OL,15,Fovertaking another vehicle."
OL,17,FMr Marr said the car "was spun to the
OL,18,Fside of the road where it caught fire".
