OL,6,F"It was not possible to release any of
OL,7,Fthe occupants and all four were
OL,8,Fpronounced dead by paramedics at the
OL,9,Fscene, whilst still in the vehicle,"
OL,10,Fhe said.
OL,12,FA pathologist's report concluded Mr
OL,13,FRoller's death "clearly involved a
OL,14,Fhead injury".
OL,16,FThe three other occupants in the car
OL,17,Fdied due to injuries "consistent with
OL,18,Fsmoke and fire gas inhalation", the
OL,19,Freport said.
