OL,3,CMotorbike overtook vehicle before head-
OL,4,Con crash that killed six, inquest told
OL,6,FIn a Facebook post written after the
OL,7,Fcrash, Mr Roller's brother Matty
OL,8,Fwrote: "I honestly don't no what I
OL,9,Fwill ever do knowing not only my
OL,10,Fbrother is no longer here but also my
OL,11,Fbest mate is also gone.
OL,13,F"Rest in peace all four of you
OL,14,Fwonderful, beautiful loving family.
OL,15,FHonestly you were the best brother and
OL,16,Fmore importantly dad any kid would
OL,17,Fever wish for."
OL,19,FThe inquest was adjourned pending the
OL,20,Fend of the police investigation.
